==Entrances and Exits==
===Entrances===
* Staring at a flickering purple light in [[level 223]] can send people to this level.

* Riding a roller coaster in [[level 995]] with a karma rating between -41 and -60 has chances of the roller coaster to lead to this level. 

* As said in the discovery section, entering a glowing purple and pink door can send one to this level, though the specified level the door is located in is currently unknown. 
===Exits===
* Though uncommon, finding a brown glowstick in the lobby area will send one to [[level 448]].

* Attempting to break the windows in the lobby until the attacker hears glass shatter will send said attacker to [[level 955]]. Using this way to leave level 452 is difficult to achieve.

* Did you know that there is a rare chance to get caught in a crowd crush during a blackout event occurring which can lead to [[level 47]]?

